{"data":[{"date":"15:44 13/08","title":"\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o\" nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/ronaldo-beo-nhap-vien-khi-di-nghi-o-tay-ban-nha.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2> Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb \u1edf Ibiza, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o 13/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1i 10/8 khi \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Celina Locks. Chi\u1ec1u 12/8, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o hai l\u1ea7n \u0111o\u1ea1t Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng tr\u1ea5n an d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn khi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o l\u00ean Twitter: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eeba nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n v\u00ec nhi\u1ec5m virus c\u00fam \u1edf Ibiza, nh\u01b0ng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t. Ng\u00e0y mai t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n\".<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo b\u00e9o nh\u1eadp vi\u1ec7n khi \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/ronaldo-1383-1534091941.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Celina trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u1edf Ibiza. \u1ea2nh: Backgrid.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nAnh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1edbi h\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3o du l\u1ecbch n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Danh th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y du l\u1ecbch t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 7 v\u00e0 thu\u00ea du thuy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng ngo\u1ea1n c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2015.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00e1ng 1/2012, danh th\u1ee7 41 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng b\u1ecb s\u1ed1t xu\u1ea5t huy\u1ebft Dengue. Khi \u0111\u00f3 anh c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi World Cup 2002 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n b\u1ec7nh li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn gi\u00e1p, khi\u1ebfn anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. </div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5441","checkdouble":"194394"},{"date":"15:52 13/08","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \"th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\" si\u00eau m\u1eabu Katie Price","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/tien-ve-dele-alli-tha-thinh-sieu-mau-katie-price.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5440","checkdouble":"194397"},{"date":"15:15 13/08","title":"C\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua \"Pogba Serbia\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/16/ac-milan-chi-110-trieu-euro-mua-milinkovicsavic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>AC Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Sergej Milinkovic-Savic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean hot nh\u1ea5t \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AC Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"AC Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/AC-Milan-rat-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lazio \u0111\u00f2i 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid, Barca, PSG, Juventus, M.U hay Man City \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n. Bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Lazio h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i l\u00ean sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u00f3. M.U v\u00e0 Man City \u0111\u00e3\u00a0b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, Real, Barca v\u00e0 Juventus v\u1eabn \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 c\u00f3 n\u00ean chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic hay kh\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>AC Milan chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u00f2n \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 th\u00ec Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n AC Milan. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Milinkovic-Savic cua Serbia\" title=\"Milinkovic-Savic cua Serbia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Juventus-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan chi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAC Milan r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 110 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Siro ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 40 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a, sau \u0111\u00f3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t \u1edf cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a 2018/19 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u euro.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo CalcioMercato, AC Milan th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Fabio Borini c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Lazio nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Milan \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-muon-juventus-mua-muc-tieu-so-1-cua-mu-o-he-2018-176-194317.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic</span>, song theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i. Juventus v\u1eeba chi 105 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ronaldo, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5439","checkdouble":"194386"},{"date":"16:29 13/08","title":"Ronaldo ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, HLV Juventus n\u1ed5 vang","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u1ed1t cho c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo m\u1edf t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i Juve</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Juventus chi t\u1edbi 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u01b0a Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Real Madrid. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Juve, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bianconeri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay Real sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3. Trong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3, anh ghi t\u1edbi 450 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 438 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Los Blancos. Ronaldo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 hung th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Juventus khi l\u00e0m tung l\u01b0\u1edbi h\u1ecd t\u1edbi 10 l\u1ea7n sau 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay t\u1ea1i Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-massimiliano-allegri-phat-bieu-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo m\u1edbi ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nG\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ch\u00ednh Ronaldo l\u00e0 t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Real v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Juventus v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Allegri m\u1eebng r\u1ee1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 22 n\u0103m qua, Juventus ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn s\u1ef1 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro, HLV Massimiliano Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 l\u1ea1c quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Massimiliano Allegri noi ve tran Real Madrid vs Juventus\" title=\"Massimiliano Allegri n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/12/hlv-juventus-neu-chung-toi-vao-ban-ket-cung-hoan-toan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Allegri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hy v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League l\u1edbn h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Scudetto, Coppa Italia v\u00e0 Si\u00eau c\u00fap Italia\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sport Italia. \u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh 5 Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League sau 5 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua v\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i g\u1eafng s\u1ee9c v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Juventus tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-khong-muon-ban-daniel-rugani-cho-chelsea-172-194073.html\">Chi ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng, t\u1ea1i sao Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 Rugani?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay-184-194164.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5438","checkdouble":"194396"},{"date":"14:38 13/08","title":"Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i  m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 n\u0103m sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a FIFA, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1edf k\u1ef3 ASIAD 2018. N\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Pakistan, Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t N h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/Thu-quan-Olympic-Pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-Olympic-Viet-N-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ecd x\u00e1t, h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ASIAD th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u0169ng v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh.\u00a0Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eebng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ed3i th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn\u201d.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Pakistan s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y mai 14/8. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 hai b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc trong tay t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194370.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguoi-pakistan-tu-tin-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194370.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Pakistan t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/12/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khong-ngai-doi-dau-dt-olympic-han-quoc-168-194334.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5437","checkdouble":"194384"},{"date":"14:57 13/08","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra qu\u00e2n \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00 chi\u1ec1u mai 14/8.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ngang ng\u1eeda Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguyen Thanh Vinh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/2/8/muon-hagl-thua-nhieu-de-kiem-nghiem-ban-linh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh mu\u1ed1n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh v\u1eabn c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ch\u1ee7 quan tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y n\u00f3i: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D Pakistan s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>V\u00ec th\u1ebf, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n cho c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>Ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra sao, nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec BHL \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n r\u1ea5t k\u0129. Th\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t sung v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i khi l\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu m\u1ea5t s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Pakistan so v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam:<em> \u201cD\u1eabu sao, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi ch\u00fang ta n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1. </em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>T\u00f4i ngh\u0129, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc tri\u1ec3n khai th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ghi b\u00e0n\u201d.</em><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Vinh c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D Asiad 2018. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1ecb chuy\u00ean gia n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0103n \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u th\u00ec h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00e0ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thu-quan-olympic-pakistan-len-tieng-truoc-tran-gap-olympic-viet-nam-168-194384.html\">Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Olympic Pakistan Saddam Hussain \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00ecnh s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i  m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5436","checkdouble":"194390"},{"date":"15:38 13/08","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/bi-chu-nha-lam-kho-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng 50 km t\u1edbi s\u00e2n t\u1eadp do n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ngay c\u1ea1nh s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh.</h2><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Sutasoma t\u1ea1i Jakarta, Indonesia. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ecf s\u00e2n ch\u00ednh n\u00ean n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed s\u00e2n t\u1eadp cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n 50 c\u00e2y s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 lo s\u00e2n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-tu-lo-san-tap-truoc-ngay-ra-quan-tai-ASIAD-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ph\u1ee5 ngay c\u1ea1nh kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, lo ng\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 di chuy\u1ec3n qu\u00e3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i, ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5h \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, BHL Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau khi nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp s\u00e2n do BTC s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp.\u00a0Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u00e2n t\u1eadp trong khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n Haper Cikarang kho\u1ea3ng 8km.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec: \"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 chi ph\u00ed. C\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm, ch\u1ecdn s\u00e2n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ASIAD s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u01a1n l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111i 4-5 ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 th\u00ec s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t\".<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018 xem th\u00eam k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao Asiad 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 12/8, do b\u1ecb b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed t\u1eadp mu\u1ed9n l\u00fac 20h00 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ee7y bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y v\u00e0 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp chay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00ea-t\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0103n t\u1ed1i, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u nay c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 16h00 \u0111\u1ebfn 17h30 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p Samsung, Cikarang. Ng\u00e0y mai (14/8), th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng D ASIAD v\u1edbi Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-viet-canh-bao-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-truoc-tran-gap-pakistan-168-194390.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia Vi\u1ec7t c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Pakistan</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Pakistan v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai, c\u1ef1u HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Vinh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5435","checkdouble":"194393"},{"date":"17:01 13/08","title":"T\u1ea1i sao Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewandowski cho Real v\u00e0 M.U?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u1ee9c","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/13/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski. Muller tin r\u1eb1ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewandowski t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga, Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia l\u00e0 Eintracht Frankfurt \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u0111\u00eam qua. Ch\u1ec9 sau 54 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Bayern \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-0. C\u1ea3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u201cH\u00f9m x\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Robert Lewandowski.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t Kingsley Coman v\u00e0 Thiago Alcantara ghi 2 b\u00e0n n\u1eefa cho Bayern. Chung cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Bavaria gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u1eafng 5-0 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Commerzbank-Arena c\u1ee7a Frankfurt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/thomas-muller-phat-bieu-ve-robert-lewandowski.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski v\u1edbi l\u1eddi khen</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Muller tin Bayern kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Lewy</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Lewandowski l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi sau 4 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Bayern. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Dortmund h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThomas Muller ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Robert Lewandowski. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Qua \u0111\u00f3, Muller hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao Bayern \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lewandowski b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Man United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/22/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span><br>\r\n<span>Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Karl-Heinz Rummenigge kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bayern Munich s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi t\u1eeb Lewandowski gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng nghi ng\u1edd\u201d, Muller n\u00f3i. \u201cAnh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng minh cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng Lewandowski \u0111ang \u1edf \u0111\u1ec9nh cao phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao CLB kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh \u1ea5y ra \u0111i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Si\u00eau c\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c, Jerome Boateng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n sang Paris Saint-Germain. V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, Muller cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n Boateng\u201d, anh n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sung m\u00e3n, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t \u00edt h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 anh \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bayern tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-phap/psg-dam-phan-chieu-mo-boateng-197-194077.html\">PSG \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-jerome-boateng-khong-phai-lua-chon-hoan-hao-voi-mu-172-194042.html\">V\u00ec sao Jerome Boateng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u1edbi MU?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-duc/bayern-khong-muon-mua-ante-rebic-193-194033.html\">M.U \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng trong v\u1ee5 s\u0103n \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-khung-bayern-chinh-thuc-tu-choi-man-united-172-194011.html\">M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-ti-nanh-voi-cac-doi-thu-khong-ngung-voi-vinh-bld-man-utd-172-193823.html\">MU thua b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c Bayern, Mourinho ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5434","checkdouble":"194398"},{"date":"15:00 13/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/them-mot-tien-dao-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Timo Werner c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Timo Werner h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Timo Werner h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Timo-Werner-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Werner l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar, Mbappe v\u00e0 Eden Hazard l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c real Madrid nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hazard.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/lich-thi-dau/real-tinh-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-eden-hazard-181-194306.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real t\u00ednh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</span>, song vi\u1ec7c k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, Real \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Rodrigo Moreno c\u1ee7a Valencia, song \u201cB\u1ea7y d\u01a1i\u201d \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 120 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Los Blancos g\u1eb7p qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u00f4ng gai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang Timo Werner</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Timo Werner c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real muon mua Werner\" title=\"Real mu\u1ed1n mua Werner\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/them-mot-tien-dao-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Werner</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Timo Werner l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a RB Leipzig, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua anh ghi 13 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 28 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Bundesliga.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Timo Werner c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c. RB Leipzig kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, song Real \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal c\u00f2n d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Timo Werner ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5433","checkdouble":"194385"},{"date":"15:44 13/08","title":"Real l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cu\u1ed7m m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u0111au l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong th\u1eddi gian kh\u00e1 l\u00e2u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Rabiot</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Andres Iniesta v\u00e0 Paulinho, Barcelona \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf. M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0 Barca t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nasser Al Khelaifi c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. Ch\u1ea3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi h\u00e3ng h\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Qatar Airways.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBarca t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Qatar Airways song g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u00e9p gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3. Kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u, g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha li\u1ec1n tr\u1edf m\u1eb7t ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 b\u1eaft tay v\u1edbi Rakuten c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, Barca \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft o\u00e1n v\u1edbi PSG. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Marco Verratti v\u00e0 Rabiot cho \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Real m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 Diario Gol c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2n hi\u1ec3m ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Barcelona. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa PSG v\u00e0 Real l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/21/Barca-muon-mua-Arturo-Vidal-voi-gia-30-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Adrien Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Real c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t \u0111i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Luka Modric. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter Milan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n b\u1ecb lung l\u1ea1c. Theo m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin, Modric \u0111ang g\u00e2y t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Modric song Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c chia tay s\u00e2n Santiago Bernabeu, Los Blancos s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Rabiot t\u1edbi PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-noi-gi-sau-khi-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-172-194240.html\">HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/ai-o-real-madrid-da-khuyen-kovacic-ra-di-cap-ben-chelsea-172-194208.html\">Ai \u1edf Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 khuy\u00ean Kovacic ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chot-eriksen-thay-modric-180-194307.html\">Real Madrid chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/them-mot-tien-dao-lot-vao-tam-ngam-cua-real-madrid-180-194385.html\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5432","checkdouble":"194389"},{"date":"16:29 13/08","title":"Real v\u00e0 Barca nh\u1eadn tin vui v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca v\u00e0 Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Adriano Rabiot c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c PSG nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/real-va-barca-nhan-tin-vui-vu-rabiot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rabiot\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-rabiot-cua-psg-180-194389.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Adriano Rabiot</span>, khi m\u00e0 Mateo Kovacic \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea c\u00f2n Luka Modric mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Inter Milan th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rabiot, ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Thomas Tuchel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, PSG v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Adriano Rabiot r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Rabiot\" title=\"tien ve Rabiot\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/154205-tien-ve-Tuchel.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Rabiot t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Rabiot v\u1edbi PSG ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i, PSG s\u1ebd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, PSG c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu Barca v\u00e0 Real Madrid th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Rabiot l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 23, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Rabiot gi\u1eefa Barca v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5431","checkdouble":"194392"},{"date":"17:37 13/08","title":"HLV Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/hlv-real-muon-co-them-2-tan-binh-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid mua th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n Real mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/hlv-real-muon-co-them-2-tan-binh-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Julen Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid mua th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u1edbi Karim Benzema, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, HLV Lopetegui c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</span> theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f2n Luka Modric c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter Milan l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T TBN mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. \u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Los Blancos nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Adrien Rabiot, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi PSG v\u00e0 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-1108-Real-mua-Thiago-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thiago Alcantara l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, Real d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN. Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm, Los Blancos t\u00ednh chi 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o, Edison Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG, Timo Werner c\u1ee7a Leipzig v\u00e0 Mauro Icardi c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111\u00f2i 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Cavani, song h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Werner c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Leipzig h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u00f2n Inter kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 Icardi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Real Madrid s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. NHM c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5430","checkdouble":"194402"},{"date":"17:01 13/08","title":"HLV Emery: \"T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man Ciy \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, ngay ph\u00fat 14 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Raheem Sterling. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Unai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/hlv-emery-toi-muon-cac-cau-thu-arsenal-co-trach-nhiem-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau hi\u1ec7p 1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady h\u1ecd c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua n\u1eefa, ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng cho Man City l\u00e0 Bernardo Silva. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 t\u1ea1i Emirates, HLV Emery c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Arsenal tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUnai Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Arsenal, \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Man Ciy \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong hi\u1ec7p 1 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e1u l\u1eeda h\u01a1n. Sau hi\u1ec7p 1 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTrong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n. D\u00f9 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 2 nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Emery xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn thua Man City cho th\u1ea5y Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, HLV Emery xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery\" title=\"HLV Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/HLV-Emery.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Emery xin th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng Man City ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Arsenal ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u1eabn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i, t\u00f4i tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 l\u1ebd t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 2 th\u00e1ng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 th\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5429","checkdouble":"194391"}]}